Custom GH3 - Guitar Hero 2 (Xbox 360 version)
DHA brings the final remake from the original Guitar Hero series
to Wii. The difference between this version and other Wii
remakes is that this version includes all songs from the 360
version of GH2, which has 10 more songs than the PS2 version.
COOP Mode is also fully functional,again, unlike other releases.
A handful of the songs are in different tiers due to filesize 
restrictions. For more information and to show your appreciation
visit www.3media.co.uk/dha
